June 2025: Package renamed script_header_joetoo and significantly enhanced
to include command higher level scripting utilities including line processor,
usage, etc in the extended [bash] header and other updates in
the basic [ash] header.  A template script showing how to use these was also
included.  First uploaded as dev-util/script_header_joetoo 24 June 2025
